Vanya Voynova (Bulgarian); December 27, 1934 March 9, 1993) bụ onye Bulgaria na agba bọọlụ basketball
Ọ gbara bọọlụ maka Slavia Sofia site n'afọ 1950 ruo n'afọ 1968, merie Ndị mmeri Europe iko n'afọ 1959 na 1963 na Bulgarian league ugboro iri na abụọ site n'ọnwa 1953 ruo n'ọnwarị 1965

Ya na ndị otu basketball ụmụ nwanyị nke mba Bulgaria, ọ meriri ọlaọcha na 1959 Asọmpi mba ụwa, ọla nchara na 1964 Asọmpi mba ụwa, odo na 1958 Asọmpi Europe , ọlaọcha n'afọ 1960 Asọmpi Europe na 1964 Asọmpi Europe na ọla nchara n'afọ 1954 Asọmpi Europe  na 1962 Asọmpi Europe  A nabatara ya n'ime Women's Basketball Hall of Fame na 2001 na FIBA nnukwu ọnụ ụlọ ndị ama ama n'afọ 2007.
Vanya Voynova gbara bọọlụ maka otu ụmụ nwanyị mba Bulgaria ruo afọ iri na ise
Ọgbọ ya ka bụ ihe na adịgide adịgide n'akụkọ ihe mere eme nke egwuregwu a na mba ahụ
Ọtụtụ ndị ọkachamara kwenyere na nke a bụ ọgbọ kachasị nwee ọganihu na narị afọ nke 20
Na Voynova n'akụkụ ya, ndị otu mba ahụ meriri otu ọla edo na otu ọlaọcha, na ọla nchara abụọ na Asọmpi Europe netiti 1954 na 1964

Noge ahụ, a na ewere ndị otu Soviet dị ka ndị kachasị mma na kọntinent ahụ, mana ndị Bulgaria meriri ndị iro ha n'afọ 1954.
Na 1959 Iko mba uwa, Voynova rụrụ ọrụ dị mkpa n'inweta ọla nchara, na-ejedebe na nkezi nke 13.1 na egwuregwu ọ bụla
Afọ ise ka e mesịrị, ọ nọ n'elu ọzọ, site n'enyemaka ya, Bulgaria meriri ọla nchara.
